  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="Aink0">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>              nīla mēṉi vāliḻai pākat</l>
<l>              toruva ṉirutā ṇiḻaṟkīḻ</l>
<l>              mūvakai yulaku mukiḻttaṉa muṟaiyē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>              All three kinds of world budded in the proper way </l>
<l>              under the shade of the two feet of one man </l>
<l>              who has as a half [the woman] with pure jewels and a blue throat (Shiva)/ </l>
<l>              who has [reserved] on his blue body a share for the woman who is a pure jewel (Vishnu). </l>
              
                        
                      </lg>
        </div>
